short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Making life that little bit easier.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
A few tweaks I use to make my life at the FI Remediation Program easier throughout the day.

Currently, this includes:
* Automatic logout disabled
* Quick mobile search
* Workspace Wall Board
* Automatic notes for phone calls
* Cleaner insurance details tab

Coming soon:
* Automatic import of call ID and phone number from IPScape to CMS

This extension has no effect on your browser outside of IPScape and CMS.

To request additional features, please message JD on Microsoft Teams.
